Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.80,0:06:57.22,udrgrd rvr,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}To a land so far away.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.60,udrgrd rvr,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}I feel the distance in-between.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.19,0:07:09.20,udrgrd rvr,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}A fragment of the world that used to be.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.61,0:07:12.57,udrgrd rvr,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Speaking through the river stream.
